snippet.title: Overwatch 2 | Loverwatch Dating Sim Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing LOVERWATCH. 

A totally real, totally non-canon dating sim hosted by Cupid Hanzo! 

Take your shot at love with Genji and Mercy this Valentine’s Day at https://loverwatch.gg!

Playable on desktop browsers! 
_
Follow #Overwatch2 for the latest news:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playoverwatch
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@overwatch
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/playoverwatch 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/playoverwatch
